    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously cared-for vehicle offers a superb blend of reliability and sophisticated style. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with responsible driving. Inside, you will find a pristine, smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seating with minimal wear and a full suite of fully operational electronics, including the premium audio and navigation systems. Under the hood, the engine runs strong and quiet, supported by a complete folder of maintenance records and a recent multi-point inspection. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With tires showing significant tread life and a recent oil change, this car is prepared to provide its next owner with years of dependable service. It is a complete, turn-key package for a discerning buyer.",
